item.content:encoded:
We’ve been working around the clock I’m an older adult who has insomnia. Will Ambien work for me? buy buyng ambien 10 mg or How the Ambien ( generic Zolpidem ) pill works? to bring enhanced support for even more formats on our source code browser.
We now support:

  • Ruby
  • Bash
  • Php
  • Python
  • Tcl
  • Latex

We revamped the branding including: menu, icon, launch screen and the way you access your projects.

Pro users can now enjoy full core spotlight support, which means you can search for your content directly into spotlight!
Full control on merge request has arrived! You can now read, write comments and also merge your merge request, directly from Gitlab Control!

As if it wasn’t enough, now it’s possible to explore public projects, add them to your favourites and even fork them!

We have also included few bug fixes to keep everything running smoothly.
